WEBVTT

00:00:01.820 --> 00:00:02.980
It's today, isn't it?

00:00:02.980 --> 00:00:04.680
Hm? What is?

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:06.240
What, you say...

00:00:06.410 --> 00:00:08.860
The results announcement of
Eden College entrance exam.

00:00:08.860 --> 00:00:12.200
It should be displayed
today at 1200 hours.

00:00:12.450 --> 00:00:14.560
This is making me nervous...

00:00:15.830 --> 00:00:19.600
My bracelet just came off...
Why today, of all days...

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.640
It's just a coincidence.

00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:24.170
L-Loid, look...

00:00:26.950 --> 00:00:31.260
Oh, come on, Yor. Black cats
equal bad luck is just a superstition.

00:00:31.260 --> 00:00:33.240
Y-You're right.

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:34.480
Father.

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:35.140
What's wrong?

00:00:35.550 --> 00:00:36.680
Anya...

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:38.060
...stepped on a poo...

00:00:40.420 --> 00:00:42.690
The results announcement of
Eden College entrance exam?

00:00:42.690 --> 00:00:45.940
Oh, the thing agent Twilight is doing, huh?

00:00:45.940 --> 00:00:51.780
Director, the course of peace between
East and West depends on Operation Strix,

00:00:51.780 --> 00:00:53.700
so you should take it more seriously.

00:00:53.870 --> 00:00:57.040
You've never met him before, have you?

00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:58.830
N-No...

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:02.910
He's considered the best spy in Westalis.

00:01:02.910 --> 00:01:04.710
So don't worry so much.

00:01:04.930 --> 00:01:08.050
Soon, he'll report that the
"cherry blossoms are blooming".

00:01:08.050 --> 00:01:09.670
What's that?

00:01:09.850 --> 00:01:11.930
It's an oriental cypher.

00:01:12.210 --> 00:01:14.060
It means "passing an exam".

00:01:15.830 --> 00:01:16.780
I can't find it...

00:01:27.980 --> 00:01:33.870
In this world like nuts packed in a bag,

00:01:33.870 --> 00:01:40.750
Everyone is snuggling up
to someone they meet

00:01:40.750 --> 00:01:46.880
We are mixed in there and smiling

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:52.550
By pretending we are
all nuts like peanuts

00:01:52.550 --> 00:01:55.470
On the template of happiness,

00:01:55.470 --> 00:01:59.020
Behind the surface
which is literally picturesque

00:01:59.020 --> 00:02:03.230
We can't be as we are,

00:02:03.230 --> 00:02:08.570
Even when we put our hands
together sitting around a table

00:02:08.570 --> 00:02:15.660
Home with full of secrets
and patches, you know?

00:02:15.660 --> 00:02:18.700
Even though I chew up
the real emotions,

00:02:18.700 --> 00:02:21.870
they still don't disappear

00:02:21.870 --> 00:02:23.460
They are still stuck in my teeth

00:02:23.460 --> 00:02:26.460
My life is so insecure and drifting,

00:02:26.460 --> 00:02:28.670
And I know

00:02:28.670 --> 00:02:32.090
Every day is so mediocre,

00:02:32.090 --> 00:02:36.890
but I'm here and so are you

00:02:36.890 --> 00:02:43.270
Just by this truth,
my stomach feels heavy

00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:51.980
(Mission: 5 - Pass or Fail?)

00:02:52.650 --> 00:02:53.760
We failed...

00:02:55.620 --> 00:02:56.610
We failed...

00:02:57.010 --> 00:02:58.490
We failed...

00:02:59.770 --> 00:03:01.720
L-Let's go home now, okay?

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:03.620
I-I'll brew us some tea.

00:03:03.870 --> 00:03:05.600
I'm sorry...

00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:07.880
It's because Anya stepped on poo!

00:03:07.880 --> 00:03:10.100
Hold it right there, Forger.

00:03:10.100 --> 00:03:10.880
Hm?

00:03:11.710 --> 00:03:13.800
Mr. Henderson!

00:03:16.470 --> 00:03:17.260
What is this?

00:03:17.540 --> 00:03:20.010
Look at the very top of the list.

00:03:20.010 --> 00:03:22.310
Anya Forger...

00:03:22.310 --> 00:03:25.100
Those are the candidates
on the waiting list.

00:03:25.100 --> 00:03:26.390
It's confidential, though.

00:03:26.980 --> 00:03:28.710
Waiting list?

00:03:28.710 --> 00:03:31.920
Correct. The overall scoring...

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:35.360
...placed Anya Forger
in first place on the waiting list.

00:03:35.610 --> 00:03:39.500
If even one of the officially
accepted candidates withdraws,

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:41.910
she'll get an immediate pass.

00:03:41.910 --> 00:03:43.080
B-But...

00:03:43.300 --> 00:03:45.160
We did something
horrible back there...

00:03:45.430 --> 00:03:49.840
Can you guess which creature
kills the most humans on the planet?

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:50.460
Huh?

00:03:51.220 --> 00:03:52.200
Mosquitoes.

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:57.250
Yes. You have saved Mr. Swan from
that dangerous creature back there.

00:03:57.250 --> 00:03:59.390
This has scored you big points.

00:03:59.580 --> 00:04:01.110
That's too much of a stretch...

00:04:01.110 --> 00:04:02.680
You should be proud, Forger.

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:05.140
You're all worthy of joining our school.

00:04:05.140 --> 00:04:09.590
If even one candidate withdraws,
Anya will pass...

00:04:09.590 --> 00:04:10.900
Correct.

00:04:10.900 --> 00:04:13.600
But what if no one withdraws...?!

00:04:13.600 --> 00:04:15.330
About that...

00:04:15.820 --> 00:04:19.060
Th-Thorn Princess?!
Why are you here?!

00:04:19.060 --> 00:04:21.350
You are Secretary Ekeniel, right?

00:04:21.350 --> 00:04:24.990
May I have the honour of taking your life?

00:04:24.990 --> 00:04:27.120
Stop! Please spare me!

00:04:27.120 --> 00:04:29.600
I have a son that will soon turn six!

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:32.200
He'll be going to Eden next month!

00:04:32.200 --> 00:04:35.010
If I die, he won't be able
to go to school anymore!

00:04:35.010 --> 00:04:37.420
I'm sorry, but that's exactly my intention.

00:04:37.420 --> 00:04:37.970
Huh?!

00:04:38.640 --> 00:04:41.520
For Anya's admission...

00:04:42.070 --> 00:04:43.300
...please die!

00:04:43.300 --> 00:04:44.260
Ahh!

00:04:44.690 --> 00:04:46.060
Wait, wait, wait! No way!

00:04:46.060 --> 00:04:48.940
You can't lay your hands
on someone innocent, Yor!

00:04:48.940 --> 00:04:49.680
Yor?

00:04:50.210 --> 00:04:52.200
I-It's nothing.

00:04:52.200 --> 00:04:54.620
I'm sorry, Mr. Ekeniel...

00:04:54.620 --> 00:04:55.170
Heh...

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:57.320
Well, after all...

00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:01.120
There are always a few who
withdraw their admission every year.

00:05:01.770 --> 00:05:04.730
Make sure you're well-prepared for that.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:07.330
Thank you very much, Sir!

00:05:09.330 --> 00:05:13.960
I may be removed from teaching
by the entrance ceremony, though.

00:05:13.960 --> 00:05:14.630
Huh?

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:18.010
After I hit that headmaster's
fat son in the face.

00:05:18.850 --> 00:05:21.110
- What kind of retribution awaits me now...
- That foolish man and this teacher...

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:24.670
I can't tell which one of them
will be most useful for the mission,

00:05:24.670 --> 00:05:28.520
but if he becomes an obstacle,
there are many ways to kill him socially.

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:31.270
Let us know if there's
anything we can help with.

00:05:31.810 --> 00:05:35.330
I appreciate your sentiment, Elegant Boy.

00:05:36.890 --> 00:05:39.440
Well, just go home and wait for the news there.

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:40.330
(3 Days Later)
Well, just go home and wait for the news there.

00:05:40.930 --> 00:05:43.350
Anya will pass!

00:05:43.350 --> 00:05:46.450
Anya will pass!

00:05:46.450 --> 00:05:47.740
- Anya will pass!

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:50.040
- What is she doing?
- Anya will pass!

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:50.820
- Looks like she's doing
- Anya will pass!

00:05:50.820 --> 00:05:51.660
- Looks like she's doing
- Anya will pass!

00:05:51.660 --> 00:05:54.520
- a ritual dance to make her pass.
- Anya will pass!

00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:56.250
- Oh, really...
- Yeah!

00:05:58.860 --> 00:06:00.070
Forger residence.

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:04.480
Yes...

00:06:05.660 --> 00:06:06.940
Excuse me.

00:06:14.540 --> 00:06:15.760
We passed!

00:06:17.510 --> 00:06:20.360
Father! Anya passed!

00:06:21.130 --> 00:06:23.220
Well done, Anya!

00:06:23.220 --> 00:06:24.200
Yay!

00:06:24.430 --> 00:06:27.900
That's great!
I'm so happy as well!

00:06:27.900 --> 00:06:30.090
Thank you as well, Yor!

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:36.670
Heya! So you passed the exam?
Let's have a drink, then!

00:06:36.810 --> 00:06:38.270
How'd you catch wind so quick?

00:06:38.270 --> 00:06:40.570
I don't work as an
informant just for show, Bro.

00:06:40.570 --> 00:06:42.830
Oh, hello, Ma'am!
Nice to meet you!

00:06:42.830 --> 00:06:45.250
I'm Franky, Loid's best friend!

00:06:45.250 --> 00:06:46.300
Hello!

00:06:46.300 --> 00:06:47.470
Curly guy!

00:06:47.470 --> 00:06:48.840
This calls for a celebration!

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:51.330
I've got some booze here,
and ordered some food, too!

00:06:51.330 --> 00:06:53.270
You and your selfish act...

00:06:53.510 --> 00:06:57.520
It's all thanks to me
stealing the answer sheets, huh?

00:06:57.940 --> 00:06:59.480
Idiot! They'll hear you!

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:03.840
Huh~? What did you say~?

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:08.380
Bro, you're not drinking enough, eh?

00:07:08.380 --> 00:07:09.290
Beat it.

00:07:09.290 --> 00:07:10.700
Good for you, Anya.

00:07:10.700 --> 00:07:13.850
Your papa just said he'll
do anything for you now!

00:07:13.850 --> 00:07:16.140
Hey! Don't promise things on my behalf!

00:07:16.140 --> 00:07:19.130
Anya wants to do something instead!

00:07:19.130 --> 00:07:20.710
Hm? What is it?

00:07:20.710 --> 00:07:22.500
Well, as long as it's within my power.

00:07:25.910 --> 00:07:28.680
Help me, Bondman!

00:07:29.290 --> 00:07:31.130
Good morning, Bondman.

00:07:31.130 --> 00:07:33.175
Your mission is to rescue Princess Honey,

00:07:33.177 --> 00:07:35.760
who has been kidnapped by
the League of Evil,

00:07:35.760 --> 00:07:37.940
and liberate the castle.

00:07:38.140 --> 00:07:40.460
Wait for me, Princess Honey!

00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:45.150
Bondman, the best spy in
the kingdom, infiltrates the castle.

00:07:45.450 --> 00:07:47.150
While destroying every enemy in his path,

00:07:47.150 --> 00:07:50.030
he finally reaches the princess.

00:07:50.030 --> 00:07:52.730
I've come to save you, Princess Honey!

00:07:52.730 --> 00:07:54.290
Bondman!

00:07:54.500 --> 00:07:57.620
They begin to nurture their love,

00:07:57.620 --> 00:07:58.070
- all while restoring peace to the castle...

00:07:58.070 --> 00:07:59.820
- Anya wants to do this.
- all while restoring peace to the castle...

00:07:59.820 --> 00:08:02.870
So you want to do...

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:06.310
Play the princess in a castle!

00:08:06.310 --> 00:08:07.220
Nope, not a chance.

00:08:10.180 --> 00:08:12.330
You're a meanie, Father!

00:08:12.330 --> 00:08:14.560
If you don't want to do it,
I won't go to school!

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:16.180
Don't speak for her.

00:08:16.530 --> 00:08:19.340
But isn't this the
Newston Castle they're using?

00:08:19.340 --> 00:08:23.400
I heard they've turned it into a theme park
for a cartoon recently, so this must be it.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:25.940
There's talks about the castle
having the same set-ups as in the show,

00:08:25.940 --> 00:08:27.240
and we can rent it, too.

00:08:27.850 --> 00:08:31.500
Now, the area around there is clear
of the government's sniffing,

00:08:31.500 --> 00:08:34.060
so it won't hurt to have a little
fun there, you know, Mr. Loid?

00:08:34.060 --> 00:08:35.040
But...

00:08:35.040 --> 00:08:37.660
Your daughter went and
passed the exam for you, though...

00:08:37.660 --> 00:08:41.880
She could use a celebration
or two to go on, you know?

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:43.040
Ugh...

00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:44.630
All right.

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:46.540
Sweet!
Let's strike while the iron's hot!

00:08:46.540 --> 00:08:49.850
I'll handle the booking,
so you handle the transport!

00:08:49.850 --> 00:08:53.060
Wait, we're going today?!
And I have to prepare too?!

00:08:53.060 --> 00:08:56.170
Well, duh!
It's for your daughter's sake, isn't it?

00:09:06.190 --> 00:09:07.600
A transmission from Twilight.

00:09:08.100 --> 00:09:10.070
Code GO005.

00:09:10.070 --> 00:09:11.970
He did it.

00:09:11.970 --> 00:09:13.280
The cherry blossoms are blowing.

00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:15.740
Another transmission from Twilight.

00:09:15.740 --> 00:09:16.450
What is it?

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:21.170
What should we do?

00:09:23.540 --> 00:09:27.340
He's considered the best spy in Westalis.

00:09:28.410 --> 00:09:29.990
See to it right away!

00:09:29.990 --> 00:09:30.700
Roger!

00:09:32.280 --> 00:09:35.430
To Falcon, Rynech District.
We have an important case from Twilight.

00:09:35.570 --> 00:09:38.890
This is Falcon.
Solid copy on the important case. Over.

00:09:39.850 --> 00:09:43.750
Gather at the lower reaches of the River
Nine, Rynech District at 1830 hours.

00:09:44.170 --> 00:09:45.720
That's a quick response.

00:09:46.650 --> 00:09:50.300
We can do stuff like this
in the castle, you know!

00:09:50.300 --> 00:09:52.210
Anya will make a quiz!

00:09:52.210 --> 00:09:54.700
Oh, that's a great idea!

00:09:54.700 --> 00:09:57.180
You rock, Bro!

00:09:57.180 --> 00:09:57.990
- This is Anya's first time on a plane!

00:09:57.990 --> 00:09:59.450
- This is sooo epic, wow!
- This is Anya's first time on a plane!

00:09:59.450 --> 00:10:00.660
- This is sooo epic, wow!
- I can't wait!

00:10:00.920 --> 00:10:02.140
This should do it.

00:10:03.670 --> 00:10:05.190
Does Anya look cool in this?

00:10:05.190 --> 00:10:06.880
Yes, you do.

00:10:07.620 --> 00:10:09.540
Loid!

00:10:09.540 --> 00:10:12.670
Where did you get this mini plane?

00:10:12.670 --> 00:10:14.460
It's so awesome!

00:10:14.460 --> 00:10:18.630
Oh, these nice colleagues
of mine lent it to me. Hahaha.

00:10:18.630 --> 00:10:21.690
Thank you for always
taking care of my husband.

00:10:24.570 --> 00:10:26.770
Put on your seat belts, people.

00:10:26.770 --> 00:10:28.010
We're taking off now.

00:10:28.010 --> 00:10:30.150
Let's go!

00:10:36.700 --> 00:10:39.920
Whoa! Anya's so excited!

00:10:42.470 --> 00:10:44.570
Yahoo!

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:50.090
Wow! So pretty!

00:10:50.090 --> 00:10:52.910
They look like treasure boxes!

00:10:52.910 --> 00:10:55.050
Father's so amazing!

00:10:59.430 --> 00:11:01.220
Hey! I can see it now!

00:11:02.970 --> 00:11:04.260
Oh, wow!

00:11:04.260 --> 00:11:05.880
- The castle's so cool!

00:11:05.880 --> 00:11:07.780
- Hey, stay put!
- The castle's so cool!

00:11:07.780 --> 00:11:10.330
I'm going to land this plane, so sit down.

00:11:13.590 --> 00:11:15.530
A castle!

00:11:15.530 --> 00:11:17.200
Don't get so excited yourself!

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:19.770
Good for them, right!

00:11:23.010 --> 00:11:23.880
What's wrong?

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:25.770
This is wrong.

00:11:25.770 --> 00:11:27.500
What do you mean?

00:11:27.680 --> 00:11:30.490
A castle without the enemy
and their servants...

00:11:30.930 --> 00:11:32.000
...is not a castle.

00:11:32.390 --> 00:11:34.180
Anya's so sad.

00:11:34.180 --> 00:11:36.510
I don't think I can go to school now...

00:11:36.510 --> 00:11:40.610
Yeah, I guess.
No one can blame you for that.

00:11:40.610 --> 00:11:42.810
Papa's got to do something
about this, right?

00:11:42.810 --> 00:11:44.310
A transmission from Twilight!

00:11:44.310 --> 00:11:47.480
He's requesting for more agents,
as many as we can get.

00:11:48.760 --> 00:11:50.960
It's a test of our strength, huh?

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:54.740
Attention, all agents in Ostania.

00:11:54.950 --> 00:11:57.990
Participate in an emergency
mission at Newston Castle.

00:11:57.990 --> 00:12:01.750
This is the most critical
agenda for Operation Strix!

00:12:01.750 --> 00:12:03.740
Mission rank: SS+!

00:12:03.740 --> 00:12:07.950
Repeat, this is the most
critical agenda for Operation Strix!

00:12:07.950 --> 00:12:10.210
Mission rank: SS+!

00:12:16.340 --> 00:12:18.710
So that's the real Twilight?

00:12:18.710 --> 00:12:19.890
I should get his signature later.

00:12:20.540 --> 00:12:22.760
So you guys can pull off this kind of
stunt when you're being wise, huh!

00:12:22.760 --> 00:12:24.520
All right, you tell them
what's going on now.

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:26.170
I'll fill them in later.

00:12:26.580 --> 00:12:27.480
Huh...

00:12:28.210 --> 00:12:29.440
All right.

00:12:32.300 --> 00:12:36.980
Ladies and gentlemen, thank you
for gathering tonight for my daughter.

00:12:38.860 --> 00:12:40.360
A Morse code?

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:43.190
"Just listen as you are."

00:12:43.190 --> 00:12:44.910
An instruction from the Twilight!

00:12:44.910 --> 00:12:45.490
I want you all to play the role of enemies...

00:12:45.490 --> 00:12:48.240
(Note that this mission is related)
I want you all to play the role of enemies...

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:50.240
(to the execution of Operation Strix,)
...of the spy wanting to rescue the princess.

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:52.500
(so there's no need for unnecessary prying.)
I don't really know what he's talking about...

00:12:52.500 --> 00:12:54.290
But we're talking about Twilight here.

00:12:54.290 --> 00:12:56.250
This mission must possess a tactical agenda.

00:12:56.250 --> 00:12:58.880
(That man you saw earlier will fill you in.)
I would be happy if you could cooperate

00:12:58.880 --> 00:13:00.340
(You will follow his instructions after this.)
for my daughter's sake.

00:13:03.260 --> 00:13:06.440
All right, time to announce
the cast for the show!

00:13:06.440 --> 00:13:08.860
Let's start with the main cast for today!

00:13:09.620 --> 00:13:11.340
Princess Anya!

00:13:12.660 --> 00:13:14.900
And the spy that will rescue Anya!

00:13:15.770 --> 00:13:16.730
Loidman!

00:13:16.950 --> 00:13:17.680
- The boss of the League of Evil,

00:13:17.680 --> 00:13:18.480
- Kerleeh!
- The boss of the League of Evil,

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:19.990
- Kerleeh!
- Professor Curly!

00:13:20.500 --> 00:13:22.750
And Mother... Uh...

00:13:23.150 --> 00:13:23.990
She's nobody.

00:13:23.990 --> 00:13:25.160
Shock!

00:13:25.350 --> 00:13:26.560
Also...

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:29.450
You guys, the skilled minions
of Professor Curly!

00:13:30.020 --> 00:13:33.450
I urge you all
to play the role as those...

00:13:33.450 --> 00:13:36.270
...who will spawn great difficulties
in Loidman's path!

00:13:36.270 --> 00:13:37.500
Huh? But...

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:39.760
The mission rank is SS+...

00:13:39.760 --> 00:13:42.700
We must clear the mission,
no matter the sacrifices!

00:13:42.700 --> 00:13:44.790
It's the real deal
if we're up against Twilight!

00:13:44.790 --> 00:13:46.980
The time's finally come...

00:13:46.980 --> 00:13:51.360
I'll leave it to you guys to
devise the plan to stop Loidman!

